name: FedEx Airbus A300-600F Evening Landing at Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Happy Heavy Aircraft Friday!
Here we have a FedEx Airbus A300 landing at Calgary International Airport, arriving from Memphis. I know I screwed up the filming right at the best part, but I still decided to upload it, since I have no footage of A300s landing anyway.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
